### Test Job API

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001
@employerToken = YOUR_EMPLOYER_JWT_TOKEN
@companyId = YOUR_COMPANY_ID

### 1. Create Job (Employer only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/jobs
Authorization: Bearer {{employerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Backend Developer",
  "description": "Chúng tôi đang tìm kiếm Backend Developer có kinh nghiệm với Node.js và PostgreSQL",
  "requirements": "- 2+ năm kinh nghiệm Node.js\n- Thành thạo PostgreSQL\n- Biết TypeScript là lợi thế",
  "salary": "15-20 triệu",
  "location": "Hà Nội",
  "deadline": "2026-12-31",
  "companyId": "{{companyId}}"
}

### 2. Get Job by ID (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs/JOB_ID_HERE

### 3. List Jobs (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs?page=1&limit=10

### 4. Search Jobs (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs/search?keyword=developer&location=Hà Nội&vipOnly=false&page=1&limit=10

### 5. Search VIP Jobs only
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs/search?vipOnly=true&page=1&limit=10

### 6. Update Job (Employer only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/jobs/JOB_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{employerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Senior Backend Developer",
  "salary": "20-25 triệu"
}

### 7. Delete Job (Employer only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/jobs/JOB_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{employerToken}}

### 8. List Jobs by Company
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs?companyId={{companyId}}&page=1&limit=10

### 9. List Jobs by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs?status=approved&page=1&limit=10
